$lang['The hexadecimal system is a base 16 number notation, while the decimal system is a base 10 number notation. In other words, the hexadecimal system uses 16 symbols to represent numbers, while the decimal system uses 10 symbols. This expansion also allows for a higher information density-hexadecimal digits can represent twice as many values as decimal digits.'] = 'Isistimu ye-hexadecimal iyinombolo eyisisekelo engu-16, kuyilapho isistimu yedesimali iyinothi eyisisekelo yezinombolo ezingu-10. Ngamanye amazwi, uhlelo lwe-hexadecimal lusebenzisa izimpawu eziyi-16 ukumela izinombolo, kanti uhlelo lwedesimali lusebenzisa izimpawu eziyi-10. Lokhu kunwetshwa kuvumela futhi amadijithi aphezulu wokuminyana-hexadecimal angamela amanani aphindwe kabili kunamadijithi wedesimali.';
