$lang['Hexadecimal is a way of representing binary data in human-readable form. It was developed in the 19th century to allow computers to store large amounts of information.'] = 'I-Hexadecimal iyindlela yokumela idatha kanambambili ngendlela efundeka umuntu. Yasungulwa ngekhulu le-19 ukuze amakhompiyutha agcine inani elikhulu lolwazi.';
$lang['You can use hexadecimal to convert between decimal and binary values. For example, converting 10011011001010 into hexadecimal would result in 0x4F. This means that the value 4F represents the binary number 100110110010110.'] = 'Ungasebenzisa i-hexadecimal ukuze uguqule phakathi kwamanani wedesimali namanani kanambambili. Isibonelo, ukuguqula u-10011011001010 kube i-hexadecimal kungaholela ku-0x4F. Lokhu kusho ukuthi inani 4F limele inombolo kanambambili 100110110010110.';
$lang['In mathematics and computer science, hexadecimal (also base 16, or hex) is a positional numeral system with a radix, or base, of 16. It uses sixteen distinct symbols, most often the symbols 0–9 to represent values zero to nine, and A, B, C, D, E, F (or alternatively a–f) to represent values ten to fifteen. For example, the hexadecimal number 2AF3 is equal, in decimal, to (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , or 10,995.'] = 'Kuzibalo nesayensi yekhompiyutha, i-hexadecimal (nayo i-base 16, noma i-hex) iwuhlelo lwenombolo yokuma olune-radix, noma isisekelo, sika-16. Isebenzisa izimpawu ezihlukene eziyishumi nesithupha, ngokuvamile izimpawu ezithi 0–9 ukuze zimelele amanani aziro kuye kweyisishiyagalolunye, kanye no-A, B, C, D, E, F (noma okunye a–f) ukumela amanani ayishumi kuya kweyishumi nanhlanu. Isibonelo, inombolo ye-hexadecimal 2AF3 ilingana, ngedesimali, no (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) noma 10,995.';
$lang['Each hexadecimal digit represents four binary digits (bits) (also called a "nibble"), and the primary use of hexadecimal notation is as a human-friendly representation of binary coded values in computing and digital electronics. For example, byte values can range from 0 to 255 (decimal) but may be more conveniently represented as two hexadecimal digits in the range 00 through FF. Hexadecimal is also commonly used to represent computer memory addresses.'] = 'Idijithi ngayinye ye-hexadecimal imelela amadijithi kanambambili amane (amabhithi) (okubuye abizwe ngokuthi &quot;i-nibble&quot;), futhi ukusetshenziswa okuyinhloko kwe-hexadecimal notation kuwumelela komuntu amanani amakhodi kanambambili kukhompyutha naku-electronics wedijithali. Ngokwesibonelo, amanani ebhayithi angasukela ku-0 kuye ku-255 (idesimali) kodwa angase amelelwe kalula njengamadijithi angu-hexadecimal kububanzi 00 ukuya ku-FF. I-Hexadecimal iphinde isetshenziselwe ukumela amakheli enkumbulo yekhompyutha.';
$lang['Hex is an abbreviation of Hexadecimal, which is based on a base -16 structure and is used for simplifying how instructions to computers are represented. This 16 symbols number system was developed as a means of inhibiting an 8-bit binary number, so data can be encoded into computers effortlessly. It can be imprinted and typed using two different hex digits with each hex digit demonstrating a nibble or perhaps a 4-bits format.'] = 'I-Hex isifinyezo se-Hexadecimal, esisekelwe kusakhiwo se-base -16 futhi sisetshenziselwa ukwenza lula ukuthi imiyalelo kumakhompyutha imelelwa kanjani. Lolu hlelo lwezinombolo zezimpawu eziyi-16 lwakhiwe njengendlela yokuvimbela inombolo kanambambili engu-8-bit, ngakho-ke idatha ingafakwa ngekhodi kumakhompyutha kalula. Ingaphrintwa futhi ithayiphe kusetshenziswa amadijithi amabili ahlukene e-hex ngedijithi ngayinye ye-hex ebonisa i-nibble noma ifomethi yamabhithi angu-4.';
$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = 'Lolu hlelo lwezinombolo lusebenzisa izimpawu eziyi-16 ezimelwe kububanzi obusuka ku-0-9 noma AF. U-0–9 umele izinombolo ezifika kweyisishiyagalolunye kanti i-AF imelwe izinombolo ezingu-10–15. Uma kuqhathaniswa nezinye izinhlobo ezintathu zezinhlelo zezinombolo, uhlelo lwezinombolo ze-hexadecimal luthathwa njengolusebenza kahle kakhulu.';
$lang['Your hexadecimal code is invalid'] = 'Ikhodi yakho ye-hexadecimal ayivumelekile';
